# Design system

Read `apps/web/DESIGN.md` for full tokens.

## Tokens

- Backgrounds: `state-void`, `state-charcoal`, `state-graphite`
- Text: `board-ink`, `state-paper`, `state-paper-dim`
- Accent: `state-amber` (authority), `state-gold` (elites/assets)
- Factions: `faction-people`, `faction-security`, `faction-danger` (events)

## Components

- Panels: `components/ui/Panel.tsx` + `lib/ui/variants.ts`
- Buttons: `components/ui/Button.tsx`
- Cards: `lib/cards/styles.ts`, `directiveCardShell`, theme art in `public/cards/themes/`

## Motion

- Durations: `lib/motion/tokens.ts` (hover ~140ms, card ~280ms)
- Variants: `lib/motion/variants.ts`
- Hand cards: `game-card-framer` / `.directive-card-hand` in `globals.css`

## Do not

- Introduce bright saturated palettes or gacha-style frames
- Animate width/height/margins on interactive cards
- Add comments to styling code unless necessary
